      "updated_at": "2026-05-21T09:30:31Z",
      "body": "But we can enhance the page table API by having more bit flags checks:\n\n```\nif page_table_entry == 0 { return None; }\nif (page_table_entry & VALID_BIT) == 0 { return None; }\n```\n\n\n\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Bit 63: NX        │ Bit 52-62: Reserved    │ Bit 51-12: PFN         │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Bit 11-9: PAT/G   │ Bit 8: Global         │ Bit 7: PAT             │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Bit 6: Dirty      │ Bit 5: Accessed       │ Bit 4: PCD             │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Bit 3: PWT        │ Bit 2: U/S           │ Bit 1: R/W             │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Bit 0: P (Present)│                                                   │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\nOr is it possible to reuse [ax-page-table-multiarch](https://docs.rs/ax-page-table-multiarch)?",
      "author_association": "MEMBER",
      "pin": null,
